  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>and\n        elbows, with...</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>Cf. Sadi, <em>Gulistan</em>: \" O\n        thou who showest virtues on the palms of the hand / But\n        concealest thy errors under the armpit / What wilt thou\n        purchase, O vain-glorious fool, / On the day of distress\n        with counterfeit silver?\"</font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"gulistan_SS.htm\"><em>Gulistan</em>,\n                6.</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"gulistan_SS.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><em>Gulistan</em> and Bleistein</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Bleistein and Misrepresentation</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Burbank and Bleistein</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "and elbows, with... Cf. Sadi, Gulistan : \" O thou who showest virtues on the palms of the hand / But concealest thy errors under the armpit / What wilt thou purchase, O vain-glorious fool, / On the day of distress with counterfeit silver?\" reference topics Gulistan , 6. Gulistan and Bleistein Bleistein and Misrepresentation Burbank and Bleistein back to \"Burbank\"",
